Class KKMQServer

java.lang.Object
  javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
          com.konakart.mq.KKMQServer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig
public class KKMQServer
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet

KonaKart MQ Server for the Application Engine. This is defined to be started in the web.xml of the konakart webapp.

This server runs an embedded Apache MQ broker which can used by the KonaKart Admin engine as well as the application engine.
